{"tid":197701,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"魚拉特航空 Overbook 直接報警拖乘客落機","createTime":"2017-04-12T04:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T05:46:27.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a14943a51519789754cb664b66757fd538e7c046","tid":197701,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"芝加哥魚拉特航空嘅作風，惹來不少乘客和網民不齒。<br />\n<br />\n據講一架飛往路易城嘅航班 Overbook，竟然搞到機艙職員問人有無自願改航班落機。<br />\n<br />\n但最後現場竟然召喚警察，將一名報稱醫生嘅人士拖下機，現場人士無不感到恐慌，甚至質問警察JM9。"},{"pid":"8583482d9f7a362e6cd6831ce68a6d9737480e7d","tid":197701,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b03e3e7aa8eb6e2e657be0305bd898d0ebe1988","tid":197701,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:46:27.000Z","msg":"魔性盡現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}